506
00:48:15,317 --> 00:48:17,199
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Perempuan ini bersenjata dan berbahaya.</i></font>

507
00:48:38,869 --> 00:48:39,838
<font color="#00ffff">Del Rio.</font>

508
00:48:39,844 --> 00:48:42,598
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Saya menerima panggilan aneh
dari seorang penduduk di Taiwan.</i></font>

509
00:48:42,604 --> 00:48:46,335
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Seorang perempuan meminta kita
membasmi perniagaan dadah besar.</i></font>

510
00:48:46,337 --> 00:48:48,382
<font color="#00ffff"><i>- Saya akan tangani.
- Baiklah, saya serahkan pada awak.</i></font>

511
00:48:48,493 --> 00:48:49,175
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Hello?</i></font>

512
00:48:49,185 --> 00:48:51,775
<font color="#00ffff">Ya, saya ada maklumat tentang
perniagaan dadah besar.</font>

513
00:48:51,777 --> 00:48:54,183
<font color="#00ffff">Saya ingin bercakap dengan pihak
berkuasa dalam tugas ini.</font>

514
00:48:54,236 --> 00:48:58,972
<font color="#00ffff">Awak bertuah, tiada lagi yang lebih
berkuasa dalam pejabat ini selain saya.</font>

515
00:48:59,006 --> 00:49:01,186
<font color="#00ffff">Tapi marilah kita mula dari awal.
Apa nama awak?</font>

516
00:49:01,188 --> 00:49:04,938
<font color="#00ffff">Dengar sini Del Rio, turunlah dari
meja dan duduk atas kerusi awak.</font>

517
00:49:05,049 --> 00:49:07,989
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Ambil pen merah sebelah kiri awak
dan catat segala maklumat yang saya bagi.</i></font>

518
00:49:14,493 --> 00:49:17,653
<font color="#00ffff">Tiada kamera, cepatlah.
Jangan buang masa.</font>

519
00:49:25,878 --> 00:49:26,896
<font color="#00ffff">Cakaplah.</font>

520
00:49:26,909 --> 00:49:30,273
<font color="#00ffff">Saya akan hantar secara terperinci
tiga orang yang akan tiba di eropah.</font>

521
00:49:30,275 --> 00:49:31,997
<font color="#00ffff">Setiap seorang membawa satu kilo dadah.</font>

522
00:49:32,797 --> 00:49:35,576
<font color="#00ffff">Saya mahu awak tangkap mereka
serta rampas dadah itu dan simpan.</font>

523
00:49:35,638 --> 00:49:38,473
<font color="#00ffff">Dadah jenis apa?
Serbuk? Kapsul?</font>

524
00:49:38,627 --> 00:49:42,514
<font color="#00ffff">Serbuk. Disorok pada plastik
dalam tubuh mereka.</font>

525
00:49:42,604 --> 00:49:43,596
<font color="#00ffff">Maaf?</font>

526
00:49:43,604 --> 00:49:45,039
<font color="#00ffff">Awak harus berhati-hati semasa mengambilnya.</font>

527
00:49:45,049 --> 00:49:46,839
<font color="#00ffff">Dadah itu mengandungi
kesan yang amat tinggi.</font>

528
00:49:53,461 --> 00:49:54,613
<font color="#00ffff">Percayalah cakap saya.</font>

529
00:49:56,128 --> 00:49:57,524
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Awak dah terima?</i></font>

530
00:49:57,645 --> 00:49:58,671
<font color="#00ffff">Ya.</font>

531
00:49:59,049 --> 00:50:00,272
<font color="#00ffff">Bagus.</font>

532
00:50:01,067 --> 00:50:02,488
<font color="#00ffff">Saya bergantung pada awak.</font>

533
00:50:06,041 --> 00:50:07,290
<font color="#00ffff">Bagaimana?</font>

534
00:50:16,620 --> 00:50:17,823
<font color="#00ffff">Selamat pagi.</font>

535
00:50:20,406 --> 00:50:21,508
<font color="#00ffff">Terima kasih.</font>

536
00:50:28,187 --> 00:50:30,905
<font color="#00ffff">Itu dia!
Tangkap dia!</font>

537
00:50:39,893 --> 00:50:41,471
<font color="#00ffff">Sila ikut kami.</font>

538
00:51:01,251 --> 00:51:02,345
<font color="#00ffff">Hello.</font>

539
00:51:03,156 --> 00:51:05,118
<font color="#00ffff">Tuan, sila ikut kami.</font>

540
00:51:21,270 --> 00:51:23,146
<font color="#00ffff">Selamat datang ke Rom.</font>

541
00:51:31,002 --> 00:51:32,509
<font color="#00ffff">Selamat pagi, tuan.</font>

542
00:51:32,552 --> 00:51:35,179
<font color="#00ffff">Sila ikut saya.
Sebelah sini.</font>

543
00:51:35,253 --> 00:51:36,420
<font color="#00ffff">Ya, tentu.</font>

544
00:51:54,121 --> 00:51:54,974
<font color="#00ffff">Del Rio.</font>

545
00:51:56,398 --> 00:51:57,612
<font color="#00ffff">Terima kasih,
saya hubungi awak semula nanti.</font>

546
00:51:57,891 --> 00:51:59,558
<font color="#00ffff">Perlukan ramai orang untuk tangkap dia.</font>

547
00:52:00,271 --> 00:52:02,361
<font color="#00ffff">Terima kasih. Saya akan hantar
fail pemindahannya.</font>

548
00:52:02,422 --> 00:52:04,113
<font color="#00ffff">Bye.</font>

549
00:52:04,238 --> 00:52:06,428
<font color="#00ffff">Baiklah, ketiga-tiganya ditangkap.</font>

550
00:52:10,694 --> 00:52:12,950
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Tuan-tuan dan puan-puan,
kita akan mula mendarat...</i></font>

551
00:52:12,960 --> 00:52:15,250
<font color="#00ffff"><i>...di lapangan terbang
Paris-Charles de Gaulle.</i></font>

552
00:52:23,715 --> 00:52:26,287
<font color="#00ffff">Cik, saya terpaksa minta anda
matikan komputer sekarang.</font>

553
00:52:26,290 --> 00:52:28,027
<font color="#00ffff">Awak patut cuci hidung.</font>

554
00:52:28,148 --> 00:52:30,793
<font color="#00ffff">- Maaf?
- Minta segelas minuman?</font>

555
00:52:32,382 --> 00:52:33,482
<font color="#00ffff">Ya, semestinya.</font>

556
00:52:37,672 --> 00:52:40,762
<font color="#00ffff">Boleh awak hantarkan segelas
minuman kepada dia?</font>

557
00:52:52,798 --> 00:52:54,836
<font color="#00ffff">Cik, minuman anda.</font>

558
00:52:56,074 --> 00:52:57,439
<font color="#00ffff">Terima kasih.</font>

559
00:52:57,702 --> 00:53:01,393
<font color="#00ffff">Maafkan saya, tapi anda perlu
menutup meja anda sekarang.</font>

560
00:53:01,978 --> 00:53:03,161
<font color="#00ffff">Tentu.</font>

561
00:53:13,009 --> 00:53:14,303
<font color="#00ffff">Untuk pengetahuan.</font>

562
00:53:25,471 --> 00:53:28,905
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Jika habitatnya tidak menguntungkan
untuk melakukan pembiakan...</i></font>

563
00:53:38,148 --> 00:53:39,973
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Sel akan memilih keabadian.</i></font>

564
00:53:45,971 --> 00:53:49,331
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Dalam kata lain, untuk efesiensi
dan menguruskan diri sendiri.</i></font>

565
00:54:05,529 --> 00:54:06,969
<font color="#00ffff">Tidak, cik, cik.</font>

566
00:54:08,997 --> 00:54:10,512
<font color="#00ffff">Anda mesti duduk.</font>

567
00:54:10,880 --> 00:54:12,058
<font color="#00ffff">Cik, hentikan!</font>

568
00:54:17,146 --> 00:54:18,216
<font color="#00ffff">Cik...</font>

569
00:54:18,494 --> 00:54:23,304
<font color="#00ffff">Cik, buka pintu! Anda perlu
kembali ke tempat duduk! Cik!</font>

570
00:54:23,871 --> 00:54:25,908
<font color="#00ffff">Kita akan mendarat.
Tolonglah, buka pintu!</font>

571
00:54:27,656 --> 00:54:29,807
<font color="#00ffff">Tolonglah cakap sesuatu.
Awak tak apa-apa?</font>

572
00:54:29,824 --> 00:54:30,855
<font color="#00ffff">Cik?</font>

573
00:54:32,978 --> 00:54:33,859
<font color="#00ffff">Cik?</font>

574
00:54:35,377 --> 00:54:37,145
<font color="#00ffff">Cik, tolong buka pintu!</font>

575
00:54:41,445 --> 00:54:43,186
<font color="#00ffff">Lakukan sesuatu.
Tolong saya bukakan pintu!</font>

576
00:54:53,791 --> 00:54:55,379
<font color="#00ffff">Saya minta awak bukakan pintu!</font>

577
00:55:04,454 --> 00:55:08,142
<font color="#00ffff">Cik, awak tak apa-apa?
Cakaplah sesuatu!</font>

578
00:55:15,844 --> 00:55:17,589
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Mereka memasukkannya
ke bahagian bawah perutnya?</i></font>

579
00:55:17,597 --> 00:55:19,917
<font color="#00ffff">Ya, kita mesti keluarkan.</font>

580
00:55:20,012 --> 00:55:22,375
<font color="#00ffff">- Perempuan itu macam mana?
- Dia selamat.</font>

581
00:55:22,377 --> 00:55:25,056
<font color="#00ffff">Dengan suntikan yang saya bagi,
dia akan terjaga sehari lagi.</font>

582
00:56:07,436 --> 00:56:10,207
<font color="#00ffff">- Doktor, dia dah bangun.
- Awak pasti?</font>

583
00:56:10,390 --> 00:56:11,898
<font color="#00ffff">Ya, dia sedang duduk atas katil.</font>

584
00:56:16,820 --> 00:56:17,877
<font color="#00ffff">Itu dia.</font>

585
00:56:17,880 --> 00:56:20,106
<font color="#00ffff">- Awak tak ikat dia?
- Dah.</font>

586
00:56:21,340 --> 00:56:23,673
<font color="#00ffff">Cik, jangan bergerak!</font>

587
00:56:24,005 --> 00:56:27,715
<font color="#00ffff">- Saya nak bercakap dengan awak sendirian.
- Dan saya nak awak angkat tangan.</font>

588
00:56:48,905 --> 00:56:50,490
<font color="#00ffff">Awak dapat bungkusan?</font>

589
00:56:52,160 --> 00:56:53,304
<font color="#00ffff">Ya.</font>

590
00:56:53,982 --> 00:56:56,489
<font color="#00ffff">- Di mana?
- Ia selamat.</font>

591
00:56:57,171 --> 00:56:59,382
<font color="#00ffff">Di sini, di Paris.</font>

592
00:56:59,482 --> 00:57:01,334
<font color="#00ffff">Bungkusan itu akan lebih
selamat bersama saya.</font>

593
00:57:19,281 --> 00:57:21,586
<font color="#00ffff">Jangan letak kereta di sana,
pergi alihkan.</font>

594
00:57:30,204 --> 00:57:32,625
<font color="#00ffff">Bagi pihak polis,
ini kes yang serius dan pelik.</font>

595
00:57:33,437 --> 00:57:35,051
<font color="#00ffff">Tapi jujurlah,...</font>

596
00:57:35,211 --> 00:57:37,641
<font color="#00ffff">...tindakan awak tadi menakutkan saya.</font>

597
00:57:38,409 --> 00:57:40,638
<font color="#00ffff">Tidurkan semua orang dengan cara begitu...</font>

598
00:57:40,664 --> 00:57:42,690
<font color="#00ffff">Patutkah kita risau terhadap mereka?</font>

599
00:57:42,986 --> 00:57:44,053
<font color="#00ffff">Tidak.</font>

600
00:57:45,453 --> 00:57:46,377
<font color="#00ffff">Bagus.</font>

601
00:58:08,233 --> 00:58:09,469
<font color="#00ffff">Awak keberatan?</font>

602
00:58:10,408 --> 00:58:11,479
<font color="#00ffff">Tidak.</font>

603
00:58:29,041 --> 00:58:32,276
<font color="#00ffff">- Apa itu?
- Bahasa Korea, biar saya pandu.</font>

604
00:58:33,905 --> 00:58:35,778
<font color="#00ffff">Tidak, tidak, tidak.
Ini kereta polis.</font>

605
00:58:35,845 --> 00:58:38,701
<font color="#00ffff">Tak boleh.
Awak tak boleh pandu, cik.</font>

606
00:58:38,703 --> 00:58:40,214
<font color="#00ffff">Ini kereta polis.</font>

607
00:58:42,339 --> 00:58:43,694
<font color="#00ffff">Baiklah, baiklah.</font>

608
00:58:51,771 --> 00:58:52,981
<font color="#00ffff">Ayuhlah, lekas!</font>

609
00:58:57,298 --> 00:58:59,805
<font color="#00ffff">Tuan, tuan, maafkan saya, tuan.</font>

610
00:58:59,807 --> 00:59:01,178
<font color="#00ffff">Saya perlu bercakap dengan seseorang.</font>

611
00:59:01,180 --> 00:59:02,801
<font color="#00ffff">Cakaplah dengan polis itu.</font>

612
00:59:03,307 --> 00:59:05,966
<font color="#00ffff">Dengar, saya warga Jerman,
saya perlukan peguam.</font>

613
00:59:06,090 --> 00:59:07,501
<font color="#00ffff">Saya mahu keluar,
awak uruskan pembedahan.</font>

614
00:59:07,594 --> 00:59:10,128
<font color="#00ffff">- Bawakan kami makanan.
- Kuat makan.</font>

615
00:59:38,160 --> 00:59:39,708
<font color="#00ffff">Awak memang selalu memandu begini?</font>

616
00:59:39,715 --> 00:59:41,382
<font color="#00ffff">Saya tak pernah memandu
lagi sebelum ini.</font>

617
00:59:41,673 --> 00:59:42,758
<font color="#00ffff">Bagus.</font>

618
00:59:48,506 --> 00:59:50,980
<font color="#00ffff">- Ini jalan sehala.
- Kita dah lewat.</font>

619
01:00:12,768 --> 01:00:14,461
<font color="#00ffff">Saya lebih suka lewat daripada mati.</font>

620
01:00:14,464 --> 01:00:15,921
<font color="#00ffff">Manusia sebenarnya tak pernah mati.</font>

621
01:01:05,714 --> 01:01:08,645
<font color="#00ffff">Maaf, tuan.
Rasanya saya tak mahu...</font>

622
01:01:15,491 --> 01:01:17,784
<font color="#00ffff">Baiklah, baiklah.</font>

623
01:01:30,476 --> 01:01:31,976
<font color="#00ffff">Saya akan arahkan mereka
supaya jangan mengekori kita.</font>

624
01:01:31,979 --> 01:01:33,134
<font color="#00ffff">Tak perlu.</font>

625
01:02:15,958 --> 01:02:17,287
<font color="#00ffff">Saya bawakan awak daging...</font>

626
01:02:55,868 --> 01:02:57,180
<font color="#00ffff">Bagi beg itu pada saya.</font>

627
01:02:58,341 --> 01:03:00,202
<font color="#00ffff">Bunuh dia dan ambil
bungkusan dadah padanya.</font>

628
01:03:17,776 --> 01:03:19,883
<font color="#00ffff">Janganlah tercegat saja,
bunuh dia!</font>

629
01:04:07,826 --> 01:04:08,870
<font color="#00ffff">Buka.</font>

630
01:04:22,594 --> 01:04:23,788
<font color="#00ffff">Mari pergi.</font>

631
01:04:23,790 --> 01:04:26,460
<font color="#00ffff">Rasanya saya tak banyak
menolong bagi awak.</font>

632
01:04:31,018 --> 01:04:32,439
<font color="#00ffff">Ya, awak boleh tolong.</font>

633
01:04:33,151 --> 01:04:34,250
<font color="#00ffff">Tolong apa?</font>

634
01:04:40,715 --> 01:04:42,281
<font color="#00ffff">Sebagai peringatan.</font>

635
01:04:43,003 --> 01:04:44,419
<font color="#00ffff">Boleh kita pergi?</font>

636
01:05:12,604 --> 01:05:13,886
<font color="#00ffff">Ke mana kita nak pergi?</font>

637
01:05:13,889 --> 01:05:15,786
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Ambil selekoh kiri pertama.</i></font>

638
01:05:17,671 --> 01:05:18,891
<font color="#00ffff">Baiklah.</font>

639
01:05:28,883 --> 01:05:32,196
<font color="#00ffff">Tidak, tidak, tidak!
Pergi dari sini!</font>

640
01:05:34,674 --> 01:05:36,651
<font color="#00ffff">Ikut kereta tadi.</font>

641
01:05:40,005 --> 01:05:42,228
<font color="#00ffff">- Profesor?
- Terima kasih.</font>

642
01:05:42,236 --> 01:05:43,862
<font color="#00ffff">- Ya?
<i>- Ini Lucy.</i></font>

643
01:05:44,149 --> 01:05:45,311
<font color="#00ffff">Ini dia, ini dia.</font>

644
01:05:47,711 --> 01:05:49,448
<font color="#00ffff">- Awak di Paris?
<i>- Ya, betul.</i></font>

645
01:05:49,453 --> 01:05:51,338
<font color="#00ffff">Bagus, bagus, sempurna.</font>

646
01:05:51,575 --> 01:05:56,363
<font color="#00ffff">Dengar, saya tiada di hotel lagi,
saya ada di universiti...</font>

647
01:05:56,366 --> 01:06:00,976
<font color="#00ffff">...supaya saya dapat kumpulkan rakan
sekerja untuk bincangkan masalah ini.</font>

648
01:06:00,983 --> 01:06:04,347
<font color="#00ffff">Pakar dalam bidang masing-masing,
dan mereka boleh dipercayai.</font>

649
01:06:04,398 --> 01:06:05,641
<font color="#00ffff"><i>Saya percayakan awak.</i></font>

650
01:06:05,741 --> 01:06:09,245
<font color="#00ffff">Terima kasih. Jadi, awak boleh
datang ke universiti sekarang?</font>

651
01:06:13,966 --> 01:06:17,388
<font color="#00ffff">Saya, gembira dapat bertemu awak.</font>

652
01:06:17,396 --> 01:06:19,098
<font color="#00ffff">Begitu juga kami.</font>

653
01:06:19,105 --> 01:06:21,371
<font color="#00ffff">- Saya Kapten Del Rio.
- Apa khabar?</font>

654
01:06:23,369 --> 01:06:26,112
<font color="#00ffff">Mari saya perkenalkan dulu
rakan sejawat saya.</font>

655
01:06:26,311 --> 01:06:28,782
<font color="#00ffff">Ini Profesor Cartier, pakar neuro.</font>

656
01:06:28,787 --> 01:06:30,513
<font color="#00ffff">- Profesor...
- Saya kenal kamu semua.</font>

657
01:06:32,237 --> 01:06:33,695
<font color="#00ffff">Semestinya.</font>

658
01:06:33,715 --> 01:06:38,055
<font color="#00ffff">Tuan-tuan, ini Lucy.
Perempuan pertama yang...</font>

659
01:06:38,207 --> 01:06:41,488
<font color="#00ffff">Maksud saya, seperti yang
saya cakap sebelum ini,...</font>

660
01:06:41,826 --> 01:06:45,440
<font color="#00ffff">...Cik Lucy masih mempunyai
perkara yang misteri bagi saya.</font>

661
01:06:45,443 --> 01:06:49,268
<font color="#00ffff">Membuka sebahagian daripada otaknya...</font>

662
01:06:49,271 --> 01:06:50,763
<font color="#00ffff">...yang mampu memberikan kita akses...</font>

663
01:06:50,826 --> 01:06:54,871
<font color="#00ffff">...untuk menjelajah bahagian
otak yang belum pernah kita capai.</font>

664
01:06:55,604 --> 01:06:58,493
<font color="#00ffff">Dia memiliki kemampuan...</font>

665
01:06:58,604 --> 01:07:00,218
<font color="#00ffff">Boleh awak tunjukkan kami contoh?</font>

666
01:07:00,308 --> 01:07:03,674
<font color="#00ffff">Anak awak Gabriel, berumur 8 tahun,
meninggal dalam kemalangan kereta.</font>

667
01:07:03,738 --> 01:07:06,005
<font color="#00ffff">Ada kereta biru,
sedang memecut laju,...</font>

668
01:07:06,106 --> 01:07:08,459
<font color="#00ffff"><i>...ada burung plastik tergantung
pada tingkap keretanya.</i></font>

669
01:07:24,493 --> 01:07:27,901
<font color="#00ffff">Bos, lima orang kita
meninggal di hospital. Maaf.</font>

670
01:07:28,838 --> 01:07:30,689
<font color="#00ffff">Berapa lagi yang masih hidup?</font>

671
01:07:30,696 --> 01:07:33,212
<font color="#00ffff">Ada 25 orang bersama saya.</font>

672
01:07:33,493 --> 01:07:36,382
<font color="#00ffff">Perempuan tak guna itu,
dia tak mudah mengalah.</font>

673
01:07:36,493 --> 01:07:37,684
<font color="#00ffff">Dia ahli sihir.</font>

674
01:07:39,927 --> 01:07:41,607
<font color="#00ffff">Saya tahu.</font>

675
01:07:42,685 --> 01:07:45,023
<font color="#00ffff">Saya sendiri akan bunuh dia.</font>

676
01:07:49,814 --> 01:07:51,767
<font color="#00ffff">Mereka datang ke sini.
Boleh awak berkawal di bilik ini?</font>

677
01:07:51,770 --> 01:07:54,039
<font color="#00ffff">- Saya mesti kekal fokus.
- Tentu.</font>

678
01:07:59,666 --> 01:08:01,039
<font color="#00ffff">Cepatlah.</font>

679
01:08:11,111 --> 01:08:13,333
<font color="#00ffff">Macam mana awak mengakses
semua maklumat ini?</font>

680
01:08:13,336 --> 01:08:15,157
<font color="#00ffff">Dengan impuls elektrik.</font>

681
01:08:15,160 --> 01:08:18,197
<font color="#00ffff">Setiap sel mampu mengetahuinya dan
berhubung dengan sel yang lain.</font>

682
01:08:18,239 --> 01:08:21,371
